Despite the repetition of similar descriptions in the provided list, it appears that all accounts refer to the same individual, Noah Carter, who set a new record in the 100m sprint at the World Athletics Championship held in Tokyo.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter is a sprinter who set a new record in the 100m sprint at the World Athletics Championship.</data>
