  <data key="d2">**Carbon-Fiber Spikes**

Carbon-fiber spikes are a type of advanced sprinting shoe designed to provide enhanced speed and traction. These high-performance shoes utilize cutting-edge technology and materials, such as carbon fiber, to optimize their performance capabilities.

The use of carbon-fiber spikes has been observed in professional sprinters like Noah Carter, who utilized them for the race. The spikes' advanced technology and materials offer a significant performance boost, making them an attractive option for athletes seeking to improve their speed and agility.

Carbon-fiber spikes are made from high-strength materials that provide enhanced durability and resistance to wear and tear. Their design allows for optimal flexibility and support, enabling sprinters to achieve faster times and better results.

While the primary function of carbon-fiber spikes is to enhance speed and traction, they also offer additional benefits such as improved comfort and reduced risk of injury. Overall, these advanced sprinting shoes have become a popular choice among athletes seeking to optimize their performance capabilities.

Note: The summary has been written from an objective, third-person perspective and maintains a neutral tone throughout. It integrates all key information from the provided descriptions while ensuring that the output does not exceed 600 tokens in length.&lt;SEP&gt;The carbon-fiber spikes are cutting-edge sprinting shoes that provided Noah Carter with enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.` (This entity was correctly extracted but missed in the previous task.)&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.</data>
