<edge source="B客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">20.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The (B客戶, C人員) relation refers to a service interaction between the customer entity "B客戶" and the personnel entity "C人員". This interaction involves providing support, maintaining equipment, and updating customers on issue status. Specifically, C人員 communicate with B客戶 as part of offering assistance, including regular updates on the progress of resolving any issues.

During these interactions, C人員 maintain open communication channels with B客戶 to ensure they remain informed about their service status at all times. The role of C人員 in this relation extends beyond support services; they are also responsible for performing routine maintenance tasks required to keep the systems used by B客戶 running efficiently and effectively.

C人員 perform various duties on behalf of B客戶, including maintaining equipment, assisting with account management, and handling maintenance needs. In addition to these responsibilities, C人員 are involved in the maintenance process for B客戶, which encompasses a range of activities such as ensuring equipment is operational and resolving technical difficulties.

Overall, the (B客戶, C人員) relation embodies a collaborative partnership between these two entities that underscores the importance of effective communication and mutual understanding in delivering high-quality service.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員has communicated with B客戶regarding account checks and generated reports for them.&lt;SEP&gt;B客戶receives maintenance from C人員.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is involved in the maintenance process for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C personnel handled B customer's maintenance record.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員also works with B客戶on maintenance tasks.</data>
  <data key="d9">communication,customer maintenance,customer notification,customer relationship,customer service,customer support,customer-employee,customer-employee relation,employee involvement,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance process,maintenance service,maintenance service provider,maintenance support,maintenance task,person client relationship,person interaction,person-organization,personnel interaction,personnel involvement,report generation,service provision,status update,technician customer interaction,technician-client relationship,technician-customer,人事安排,維護工作</data>
