<edge source="C人員" target="E客戶">
  <data key="d7">22.0</data>
  <data key="d8">**Entity/Relation: (C人員, E客戶)**

(C人員, which translates to 'C personnel' or 'C staff,') plays a crucial role in handling various tasks related to E客戶, or 'E customer,' maintenance. Specifically, C人員 provides maintenance services to E客戶, performing tasks such as handling their maintenance needs and responsibilities. The technical team from C人員 will be directly involved in addressing the maintenance requirements of E客戶.

C人員's role encompasses a range of activities including but not limited to: assigning personnel for specific maintenance tasks assigned to E客戶, providing maintenance services to ensure that all issues are adequately addressed, handling maintenance tasks on behalf of E客戶, and performing technical work related to E客戶's upkeep. This involvement is crucial in maintaining the optimal functioning of E客戶 and ensures their continued operational efficiency.

C人員 handles various aspects of E客戶's maintenance requirements, including system maintenance, such as Splunk system maintenance. They also provide support for E客戶's system maintenance needs, ensuring that all issues are adequately addressed. In addition to these tasks, C人員 is responsible for handling maintenance requests from E客戶 and performing maintenance on their systems.

In summary, (C人員) plays a critical role in managing E客戶's maintenance requirements, indicating a close working relationship between these two entities for the effective management of E客戶's technical aspects.&lt;SEP&gt;The technician, C人員, handled the maintenance for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is assigned to handle the maintenance services for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is responsible for handling E客戶's maintenance needs.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員handles E客戶's maintenance tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員performs maintenance for E客戶.</data>
